fields.name: Hritik
fields.message:
Ml is a domain in innogeeks.  I want to know whether they have a different batch for an AI (mainly deep learning )student BCS traditional Ml algo and DL algorithms are different things. Or we are going to learn about python in the same batch.
(From 2nd year student)
fields.subject: AI/Ml
fields.email_subject: Query Regarding Teaching Curriculum in ML Domain
fields.email_body:
Hi Hritik,
At Innogeeks we start off with Python and then we deep dive into Machine Learning algorithm's and it's supported libraries in Python. Since deep learning is a very vast and advanced topic and somewhat beyond the scope of graduation level, hence we confine ourself to machine learning. Nonetheless, we have mentors in innogeeks to guide you in deep learning and AI if you are stuck somewhere.
I hope we are able to clear your doubts.

Thanks,
Team Innogeeks
